  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd 15 \u0b86\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8 - \u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Holiday for all schools till 15th - Ministry of Education",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education has decided to grant a holiday to all schools nationwide from tomorrow (11) to 15 July.",
        "A decision in this regard was taken during the discussion held between the education authorities as the ongoing transport difficulties along with the fuel crisis are hampering education.",
        "The Ministry of Education has announced that all schools will be opened on Monday, July 18."
      ],
